title: super mario all stars pc emulator
description:
Super Mario All Stars and World easy install

  I take No Credit for this,    It was recieved from another source.

       Works with a 360 contoller after configure.

simply install the game and enjoy,

for controller setup, be sure controler drivers are allready installed and 
                                                                                
functions, start game, once game is running press ESC. A small menue comes up, 

using mouse click on CONFIG, then INPUT, go to each controle and inpute the 

buttons one at a time. ex... up press up on controller, down press down on 

controller, continue for all other bottons. When finished press exit on small 

menue only, then press ESC. to continue game.


enjoy...
